IMAPAccount hello
Host mail.privateemail.com
Port 993
User hello@ryanlue.com
PassCmd "pass web/email/hello@ryanlue.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

# lists@ryanlue.com -----------------------------------------------------------
IMAPAccount lists
Host mail.privateemail.com
Port 993
User lists@ryanlue.com
PassCmd "pass web/email/lists@ryanlue.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

# rl@zammad.com ---------------------------------------------------------------
IMAPAccount zammad
Host mx1.zammad.com
Port 993
User rl@zammad.com
PassCmd "pass web/email/rl@zammad.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

# STORES ======================================================================

IMAPStore gmail
Account gmail

IMAPStore hello
Account hello

IMAPStore lists
Account lists

IMAPStore zammad
Account zammad

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/\<\<Gmail\>\>
Flatten "."

# CHANNELS ====================================================================

Channel hello
Master :hello:INBOX
Slave :local:<<Hello>>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel lists
Master :lists:INBOX
Slave :local:<Lists>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel zammad
Master :zammad:INBOX
Slave :local:<<Zammad>>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail:INBOX
Slave :local:<<Gmail>>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :local:<Drafts>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :local:<Sent>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-spam
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :local:<Spam>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-deferred
Master :gmail:"Deferred"
Slave :local:<Deferred>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-dumplock
Master :gmail:"Dump Lock"
Slave :local:<Dump-Lock>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :local:<Trash>
Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel gmail-labels
Master :gmail:
Slave :local:
Patterns * !"%" ![Gmail]/*
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# GROUPS ======================================================================

Group inboxes
Channel hello
Channel lists
Channel zammad
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-deferred
Channel gmail-dumplock

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-spam
Channel gmail-deferred
Channel gmail-dumplock
Channel gmail-trash
Channel gmail-labels
